{"tid":93384,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"(正能量)一齊講下人生中最窮最折墮最慘係點過","createTime":"2017-01-24T11:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-24T12:08:32.000Z","uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b206c07fc4df53405c514cc14b9014f4a9b12f3","tid":93384,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:19:37.000Z","msg":"大概十年前<br />\n當時中學唔乖讀到中途冇讀<br />\n我本身個性格又比較倔<br />\n屋企環境唔好 冇問雙親拎錢洗<br />\n之後我扮翻工.實質留連公園.女朋友又走埋<br />\n屋企人食晚飯既時候我講大話話出街食<br />\n最後翻到屋企睇下有冇剩飯剩菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時餓到頂唔順屋企又冇野食既時候拎支麻油入房<br />\n係咁奶支麻油個蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢段日子大概維持左半年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4136fbf603e4ff60d1277aad972db545f0d89a9b","tid":93384,"uid":33770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:21:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d1a2daf71351bc82a5d79096f9e104ee71702e","tid":93384,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:35:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d238fdb03c80de36527f274d076c0afd1a53db5c","tid":93384,"uid":6327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aed54dc58e3e762eee74fbffa80b6d6d2b8d58f","tid":93384,"uid":38194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T11:59:10.000Z","msg":"一支煙5個人輪，我排第五<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d003eaab619530632c1e937fa0164233a59a025","tid":93384,"uid":3066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T12:01:51.000Z","msg":"覺得自己做果份工已經慘過做狗，點知琴日睇到個post原來樂多人都係欣榮花園2,3樓返工，覺得佢地仲慘"},{"pid":"7f7fef2e4bbdaf43c9334153f69ddca47f6888ab","tid":93384,"uid":3066,"like":0,"di